{"tid":1473734,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"鍵盤戰士有感","createTime":"2019-08-15T02:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T04:30:53.000Z","uid":178332,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"99cd179f84c904ad1ad90fb1a81c3b7c44ae9dbb","tid":1473734,"uid":178332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:39:20.000Z","msg":"其實你地有冇諗過可以用返對家嘅招數<br />\n例如標籤姓付嗰條撚樣做恐怖分子<br />\n「香港市民機場捉拿藏有武器（與早前恐襲同款）恐怖分子」<br />\n「中共恐怖主義政權包庇親共恐怖分子 美化為記者（付某持雙程證 並無工作許可） 滲入香港」<br />\n合情合理<br />\n拿話說當年啲真。恐怖分子畀人殺頭<br />\n我真係冇咩同情心 會覺得佢地罪有應得<br />\n可唔可以多啲人陪我一齊講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重有稱呼香港警察<br />\n已經唔可以再叫警犬<br />\n可以叫「穿著香港警察制服 操內地方言 無法提供委任證的武裝恐怖分子」（係長咗少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請隨便copy save低）<br />\n唔該晒咁多位"},{"pid":"1e3d665935a6d28b72ebfbb0523971be9ba586c3","tid":1473734,"uid":160268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"柒少陣啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1830a3e7cd5d2c88542c90387e1c581260542f7d","tid":1473734,"uid":178332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e3d665935a6d28b72ebfbb0523971be9ba586c3","tid":1473734,"uid":160268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:40:12.000Z","msg":"柒少陣啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T04:30:53.000Z","msg":"可唔可以畀個理由黎等我死得眼閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}